lines: 1. Jawar Yesu itelnae ngimana mar chandruokGapaka mogingore,masiche be mopondoIn Jaloch maduong` mar nam,Jawar Yesu itelna.
2. Kat` apaka gingore,Inyalo kueyo yamo.Apaka mager winjikichiko mondo gikwe.In Jaloch maduong` mar nam,Jawar Yesu itelna.
3. Ka achiegni gi chopo,ka yembe malich kudhoEdho nam mokwe maber,ka ayiengora kuomi Yie,Awinji kiwachona,"Kik iluor anatelni."
